\v 13 Then\f + \fr 1:13 \ft Hebrew “And” \f* let our appearances and the appearance of the young men who are eating the fine food of the king be compared ⸤before you⸥,\f + \fr 1:13 \ft Literally “in your presence” \f* and \add then\add* deal with your servants ⸤according to what you see⸥.”\f + \fr 1:13 \ft Literally “and according to/that you see” \f* 
