\v 16 ⸤So⸥\f + \fr 1:16 \ft Literally “And it happened” \f* the guard ⸤continued to withhold⸥\f + \fr 1:16 \ft Literally “he was … withdrawing” \f* their fine food and the wine of their drink, and he gave them\f + \fr 1:16 \ft Hebrew “to them” \f* vegetables.
