\v 34 “But at the end of ⸤that period⸥,\f + \fr 4:34 \ft Literally “the day” \f* I, Nebuchadnezzar, lifted up my eyes to heaven, and \add then\add* my reason returned to me; and I blessed the Most High and ⸤the one who lives forever⸥\f + \fr 4:34 \ft Literally “\fq the one \ft living forever” \f* I praised and I honored.
