\m 
\v 1 Belshazzar the king made a great festival for \add a\add* thousand \add of\add* his lords,\f + \fr 5:1 \ft Or “nobles” \f* and ⸤in the presence of⸥\f + \fr 5:1 \ft Literally “to over against” \f* the thousand \add lords\add* he was drinking wine.\f + \fr 5:1 \ft Or “the wine” \f* 
