\v 28 ⸤This is the end of the account⸥.\f + \fr 7:28 \ft Literally “Up to here \fq is \ft the end of the account” \f* ⸤As for me, Daniel⸥\f + \fr 7:28 \ft Literally “I Daniel” \f*—my thoughts terrified me greatly and my face changed over me, but I kept the matter in my heart.”\f + \fr 7:28 \ft Or “to myself” \f*
\c 8
\s1 The Vision of a Small Horn that Oppresses Israel and Threatens the Temple
\m 
